Metric: April Sales (CSV)
Description: Total sales revenue for completed orders in April 2026, read directly from a CSV export. A minimal end-user example — no database required, just a spreadsheet-style file.
Owner: demo
Tags: demo, csv, revenue

Source: sales

Given all records from the sales table
  And status is "completed"
  And amount is present
  And order_date is within April 2026

When we calculate
  Then sum the amount column across qualifying orders
  And round to 2 decimal places

The result is "April Sales"

Trust:
  Freshness must be less than 24 hours
  Null rate on amount must be less than 5%
  Null rate on order_id must be 0%
  Value must be between 1000 and 100000
